{"type": "article", "id": 28723, "title": "没有拉链的行李箱", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-27T06:51:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 96, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163254bqP2G8F5ziTJ4fW9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>还记得我们之前介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28053.html\">会爬楼梯的行李箱</a>吗？今天介绍的 Trunkster 也是一个打破传统的设计。整个箱体采用了航天铝材制作，将用防水防磨材料制成的活动门帘替代了拉链，在过安检时可以非常快速地取出想要的东西，不需要再手忙脚乱地翻找了。它的拉杆也很有特色，延伸到行李箱两边的设计可以让人在保持平衡的同时轻松地滑动。由于内置电子秤，提起后能够直接在把手的显示屏上读到行李重量，而且还可以切换单位。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.trunkster.co/products/trunkster\">购买链接</a>，售价为 435 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163252rFspuj1wzD4A5XyW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163253m78IiKFEo1gN5Lkn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163253khiOpZjrWXK8Acdw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163254K2uDSZeraRsojb9q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}